rComments: LOVE this prof! I hated English before taking this class! I wish I could have her as a prof again in the future :)
Really nice teacher. She was strict but always clear and wanted to best for her students.

She really knows how to get the best out of her students. She was clear and to the point with her teaching and expectations and chose assignments and stories well suited for students. It is a very interactive class and the more you participate, the better you will do. Always willing to help, and gives excellent feedback on assignments.

Favourite prof by far! Even though she has high expectations for her essay assignments, she provides a page or more of hand written feedback. If you follow it, you will improve. I would love to be in a class of hers again!
LOVED this prof! I hated English prior to taking this course...she is very helpful and wants the best for her students!
Very picky marker. She will know your first and last name by the second week of classes guaranteed. Extremely useful feedback on essays. Awesome prof all round!

Prof Bajwa is actually a great professor. At first I felt a bit of anger towards her because she is a very picky marker, but I soon realized that her points were legitimate and that I have learned a lot throughout the course. One thing to make sure of is to work extremely hard on your essays, she sees EVERYTHING!

HATED ENGLISH or ESSAY WRITING prior to her classes. she's very funny managed to make a oring class into a an interesting class. learned a lot from her feedbacks and students really improved with her teaching. 5 stars professor!!
